This is the story of Bosnian diver Sanja Mitric.  I am proud to finally share a special global campaign we worked on for @nature_org The Nature Conservancy at @tentfilm . It is one of those dream meaningful projects. We were given the task to produce 8 short films about river champions and guardians, from scientists to locals who are trying to protect rivers in the Balkans. We spent most of this June on the field, working in 5 Balkan countries: North Macedonia, Serbia, Bosnia and Herzegovina, Croatia, and Montenegro.

